title: Kranium Feat. Tory Lanez "We Can" Video
text:
Posted by Devon Jefferson  32pm Subscribe to HNHH TV Dancehall superstar Kranium links up with Tory Lanez in the video for "We Can." 
Last August we received the Tory Lanez assisted single "We Can" and after months, Kranium has finally connected with Fargo for the official video for the track. 
The video is 100 percent the visual representation of the track as Kranium and Tory get real cozy with a slew of ridiculously gorgeous women. These visuals make you feel some type of way as silhouettes of curvaceous women cascade off of the silky texture of the flowing sheets suspended throughout. 
In addition to releasing this video, Kranium also announced extended tour dates that you can check out in the tweet below while you vibe out to these new visuals.
